    \"skill\" : {
      \"check\":\"false\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Swear an Iron Vow[/i] by kneeling and grasping your sword's blade, add +1 and take +1 momentum on a hit. If you let the edge draw blood from your hands, [i]Endure Harm[/i] (1 harm) in exchange for an additional +1 momentum on a hit.\"
    }
  }
  
